{"tid":1550690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人話佢好想出名想借連登上位咁話","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T06:07:51.000Z","uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b64ec8a0a371ca6748b8ae4f1221360f6483322","tid":1550690,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"暫時放鬆下先香港嘅朋友仔，小弟第一條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔多講，借連登上位不嬲係死罪<br />\n仲要講到自己好撚巴禁，無follow佢ig好似好有問題咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e0588d0d10d278a9404b5f4f26106909b555de","tid":1550690,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b64eaf0ce205bc3ed40c6f6570a02539b6fb86cb","tid":1550690,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"樓主柒夠未"},{"pid":"83e6c08d7c4268a75e2db3e744be5ad2e7ab9eed","tid":1550690,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64eaf0ce205bc3ed40c6f6570a02539b6fb86cb","tid